snippet.title: Pokemon Cafe ReMix - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Pokemon Cafe ReMix launch trailer. Pokémon Café ReMix, a revamp of Pokemon Cafe Mix, is available now on the Nintendo eShop, Google Play, and the App Store. Watch the Pokemon Cafe Remix trailer for a look at what to expect with the game, featuring new game modes, refreshed gameplay, and more Pokémon.

#IGN #Gaming #Pokemon
